    "english_name": "Ludvig",
    "english_desc": "Leader of the Lonely Jackals. He already had a bad reputation as an opportunist, but none expected him to change so drastically after Jian fell. Clinging to the strong while harboring ugly ambitions, he dreams of one day trampling over those he stabbed in the back and standing at the top."
