    "internal_name": "BuffLevel_Passive_Karanda",
    "suffix": "Karanda",
    "size": 414,
    "english_name": "Karanda",
    "english_desc": "The queen of the Harpies. She resides in Silver Wolf Mountain. Harpies are fiercely territorial and would sometimes threaten humans who wander near, but the queen never took much interest in humans. However, she has recently gained infamy for rading and plundering travelers in a fit of fury as an effort to seek out the human who stole her egg."
  },
