    "size": 416,
    "english_name": "Primus the Ancient",
    "english_desc": "An Ancient returned to the world through the power of an Artifact.<br/>At the Three Brothers' Cliff dwells a legendary being said to hurl resisting foes into raging whirlwinds. Legend foretells that when it reunites with its comrades, it will conquer the entire continent."
