    "english_desc": "An ancient being returned to the world through the power of an Artifact.<br/>Legends tell that in Five-Finger Mountain dwells an Ancient capable of freely commanding massive stones. When reunited with their comrades, it is said they will conquer the entire continent of Pywel."
  },
